{
  "about": "I'm a veteran who served for 10 years. I joined Endurance to share my experiences and support fellow veterans dealing with PTSD."
}

### 25. Validation: about exceeds 500 characters – should return 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me/about
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "about": ""
}

### =====================================================
### Image
### =====================================================

### 26. Update image for current user (VETERAN)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me/image
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "https://example.com/my-profile-picture.jpg"
}

### 27. Validation: empty image – should return 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me/image
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": ""
}

### 28. Verify profile fields are returned after updates
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}

